      </p>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S5LV0657P0-02785'>
        <a name='S5LV0657P0_20040115_GCR_112'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-robert-maclennan' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0657P0_20040115_GCR_112' title='Link to this speech by Mr Robert Maclennan' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
